{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "c9b60b7d-1f0b-4df5-a920-3ffb4d6e6f61",
    "name": "Reward System Backend",
    "description": "API collection aligned with OTP-only authentication (2026).\n\n**Public auth:** `POST /auth/otp/request` (returns `devCode` in non-production) → then one of: `auth/superadmin/otp/signup` (web, only if no Super Admin), `auth/admin/otp/signup` (Ops self-register → pending approval), `auth/admin/otp/login` (Super or approved Ops), `auth/customer/otp/signup`, `auth/customer/otp/login`.\n\n**Ops approval:** Super Admin (Bearer) → `GET /admin/operational-admins/pending` → `POST /admin/operational-admins/:id/approve`.\n\n**JWT:** All non-`@Public` routes require `Authorization: Bearer` (e.g. Support, app home, profile).",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth (public)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "OTP Request (SMS stub; saves devCode in dev)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/otp/request",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "otp", "request"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"countryCode\": \"{{countryCode}}\",\n  \"phone\": \"{{otpPhone10}}\"\n}\n"
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('otp request', function () {",
                  "  pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.be.oneOf([200, 201]);",
                  "  const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.expect(json).to.have.property('otpSent', true);",
                  "  pm.expect(json).to.have.property('requestId');",
                  "  if (json.devCode) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('mobileDevOtp', String(json.devCode));",
                  "  }",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Super Admin — OTP Signup (web; fails if Super Admin already exists)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/superadmin/otp/signup",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "superadmin", "otp", "signup"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"countryCode\": \"{{countryCode}}\",\n  \"phone\": \"{{superadminPhone10}}\",\n  \"code\": \"{{mobileDevOtp}}\",\n  \"fullName\": \"{{superadminFullName}}\",\n  \"email\": \"{{superadminEmail}}\"\n}\n"
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "  const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "  if (json.accessToken) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('superadminAccessToken', json.accessToken);",
                  "  }",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Management — Admin OTP Login (Super Admin or approved Ops Admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/admin/otp/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "admin", "otp", "login"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"countryCode\": \"{{countryCode}}\",\n  \"phone\": \"{{otpPhone10}}\",\n  \"code\": \"{{mobileDevOtp}}\"\n}\n"
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('admin OTP login', function () {",
                  "  if (pm.response.code === 403) {",
                  "    // Ops Admin pending Super Admin approval",
                  "    return;",
                  "  }",
                  "  pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.equal(201);",
                  "  const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.expect(json).to.have.property('accessToken');",
                  "  if (String(pm.collectionVariables.get('otpPhone10')) === String(pm.collectionVariables.get('superadminPhone10'))) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('superadminAccessToken', json.accessToken);",
                  "  } else {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('opsAdminAccessToken', json.accessToken);",
                  "  }",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Ops Admin — Self signup (phone + OTP; returns pendingApproval, no token)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/admin/otp/signup",
